dji.sdk.api.GroundStation

Class DJIGroundStationTypeDef

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.GroundStation.DJIGroundStationTypeDef

  • public class DJIGroundStationTypeDef
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Ground Station Type Define Class

    This class file will contain some enums for groundstation usage. Developer could use the enum to recognize the status of groundstation task or to set up the preference.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
